commit af85a17d1d1e25148bda60a8ff3e6c689ebd95fa
Author: mschoenlaub <manuel.schoenlaub@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Mar 1 20:09:14 2015 +0100

    Adds a test for the disposal of old connections from the connection pool

