    The batch size needs to be tweakable between getmores
    
    Added:
    uint32_t mongoc_cursor_get_batch_size (const mongoc_cursor_t *cursor)
    void mongoc_cursor_set_batch_size (mongoc_cursor_t *cursor, uint32_t batch_size)
    
    Closes #120

